Package: afnireg
Type: Package
Title: AFNI Integration for fMRI Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-15
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre]
Authors@R: 
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", 
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Provides an R interface to AFNI's 3dDeconvolve program for fMRI 
    analysis. Allows users to specify complex experimental designs and HRF 
    models in R using the fmridesign framework and execute them using AFNI's 
    optimized estimation routines. Supports multiple HRF basis functions,
    censoring, nuisance regression, multi-run designs, and contrast testing.
